      507.62,
      538.53,
      571.73
    ],
    "text": "Issued at 04.00 p.m. on 17 April 2026. Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa and Southern provinces and in Nuwara-Eliya districts after 1.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
